Package de.rwth.swc.coffee4j.junit.engine.annotation.configuration.sequential.generation.configuration

Annotation Type ConfigureIpog

  • @Documented
@Target({ANNOTATION_TYPE,METHOD})
@Retention(RUNTIME)
@ConfigurationSource(provider=IpogConfigurationProvider.class,
                     configurable=Ipog.class,
                     configuration=IpogConfiguration.class)
public @interface ConfigureIpog
    This is an annotation to configure the Ipog TestInputGroupGenerator via IpogConfiguration. It defines a ConfigurationSource with the IpogConfigurationProvider to create new instances of a IpogConfiguration.

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element Description
      Class<? extends ConstraintCheckerFactory> constraintCheckerFactory
      Gets the class of the ConstraintCheckerFactory
